  <brief_title>An Explorative Trial to Evaluate the Pharmacodynamic Effect of SPD557 on Reflux Parameters in Refractory GERD Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Explorative, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, DB, Parallel-group Trial, to Evaluate the Pharmacodynamic Effect of SPD557 on Reflux Parameters in Subjects With GERD &amp; With Persistent Symptoms Despite Taking a Stable Dose of PPIs</official_title>
