  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to investigate the pharmacodynamic effect on reflux parameters
      of SPD557 tablets (0.5 mg t.i.d., on top of PPI treatment) in patients with Gastroesophageal
      Reflux Disease (GERD) with persistent symptoms despite taking a stable dose of proton pump
      inhibitors. Additionally the effect on symptoms will be explored and safety and tolerability
      will be evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
